                     <layoutDesc>
                        <layout columns="2" writtenLines="42">In double columns, each column
                              <dimensions type="column" unit="mm">
                              <height min="213" max="215">213–15</height>
                              <width quantity="62">62</width>
                           </dimensions>, with <dimensions type="intercolumn" unit="mm">
                              <width quantity="15">15</width>
                           </dimensions>between columns, in 42 lines to the column. No prickings;
